column1: i feel like i've been run over by a truck
resting pulse had jumped to about 120
needed to rest every few minutes
on the back of the head pain in every tendon
tightness in throat with occasional choking problem
not being able to get out of bed in the morning
lost all sexual desires and thoughts
loss the will to do anything
no amount of sleep makes me feel rested
vision problems - seeing two or three of everything
pain in my lower legs and feet
right hand has been getting numb
difficulty walking due to swelling in legs
tingling on left side of face
hert from head to my toe
tingling in the soles of my feet
muscle twitching on bottom of feet
pain when i sit down or stand from a sitting position
hot/heated flushing sensation that began mid-torso and continued up to the top of head (top of scalp started tingling and burning)
worse headache than usual (i have migraine)
leg joint pain similar to arthritis
like im in a fog all the time
pain in my arm and shoulder
severe pain close to my the crotch area
pain in muscles of both upper arms
generaly feeling unwell like walking in a daze (zombie like)
unable to even climb 1 flight of stairs
